    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini Dei et salvatori nostri Iesu Christi. <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">lmperantibus</rs> domnis nostri <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/118">Lodovvicus</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/9">Lothtarius</persName> filius eius
                        divina ordinantes providentje magnis imperatoris agusti, Deo propitjus annis
                        regnis eorum vigisimo quarto et octavodetjmo, die quintodetjmo mense
                        dicenbrio, indictjone prima. A vobis vir venerabilem domno <persName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Abbots" ref="#people/199"
                            >Ansfrido</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> sanctorum omnium apostulorum et
                        Christi confessorum <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Rent_in_kind #Actionarii/actores #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47">Silvestri</orgName> sito <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Nonantolas</placeName>
                        <rs key="#City_territory">terretorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/38">Motinense</placeName>,
                        peto ego <persName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Agricultural_workers #Freeborn"
                                ><name ref="Iohannacis">Iohannace</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Mauruntus">Maurunto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">livero homo</rs> ut mihi seo et ad filiis mei <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">livellario et massaritjo
                            nomine</rs> ad lavorando et iusticia domnica persolvendo dare nobis
                        iubeatis rem iuris sagri monasterii vestri in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fundi #Petiae #Wood #Forests #Houses #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Land_clearing #Rent_in_kind #Cereals"
                            ref="#places/2492">Ostilia</placeName> terretorio <placeName
                            key="#City_territory" ref="#places/59">Veronense</placeName>, prope <rs
                            key="#Rivers">fluvio Pado</rs>. Idest una <rs key="#Petiae">petja</rs>
                        de terra ad iugem vigenti exarata cum <rs key="#Wood">arboribus</rs> et [..
                        11..] super se abente in integrum. Et est ipsa petja mensurata lungo ipso
                        fluvio Pado, ad pertica legitima, perticas septuaginta: de uno latere finem
                            <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/275">Mantuana</placeName>
                        abente, et de alio latere <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">lohanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs> vestro abente, uno capite Pado
                        percorrente, qualiter percorrente in <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs> ubi ipsa
                        fine coniuxeri, de supradicti viginti iugem finem coniuxerit. De quibus
                        superius nominatis rebus promittimus adque spondimus pueriter et fideliter
                        sine omnes nelicto vel fraude lavorare et excollere et superabitare ad annos
                        viginti et nove, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> in ibidem restaurare, curte et
                            <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto</rs> claudere, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineas</rs> pastenare et propaginare, <rs key="#Land_clearing">silva
                            infructuosa roncare</rs>, cethtera salvare, finem deffensare, ut in
                        omnibus suprascriptas rebus meliorentur nam non peiorentur. Et <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_kind">redere vobis et parte monasterii</rs> vestri exinde
                        annue promittimus de omnem lavorem quem ibidem Dominus dederit aut in ipsa
                        terram <rs key="#Cereals">seminatum</rs> fuerit: in canpo cappa quarta, de
                        menudu modio quarto trituratus in areas cum nostro dispengio, lino manna
                        quarta, et si vites posuerimus exinde anfora quarta; <rs key="#Exenia"
                            >exenio</rs> vero in natale Domini <rs key="#Poultry">pullo</rs> bono
                        uno, ovas quinque, et in pasca Domini pullo duos, ovas decem, et in sancti
                        Martini dinarios decem. Per anno <rs key="#Operae">opere</rs> manualiter sex
                        cum annona domnica in Ostilias [..2..] suprascripto omnem reditum vegere et
                        consignare in <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cella</rs> vestra in <placeName
                            key="#Cells/hermitages #Operae #Exenia" ref="#places/1538"
                            >Piscaria</placeName> cum nostro dispengio; et per tenpus lavoris vino
                        recolliendo, misso domnico susscipere et susscepta eis facere et braciatica
                        eis dare promittimus. Et sit de hec ista omniam minime fetjerimus per <rs
                            key="#Actionarii/actores">misso et actore monasterii</rs> vestri
                        districti et pignorati esse debeamus. Penam cotdem anbas partis ponimus ut
                        sit quas pars partis contra os livello te[nt]avimus [..5..] ex[ire] vel
                        minare ante stetuto tenpus voluerit, aut qualives inpositjionem facere
                        quesierit, tunc promittimus conponere pars partis fidem servantis solidos
                        vigentis et pos conposito pena preseo os livello in suam maneat firmitatem.
                        Acto in Piscaria pro suprascripta indictjone. Signum + manus Iohannatj quit
                        ipso suprascripto livello fierit rogavit, cuit relictum est. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Signa +++++ manus</rs> manus manus manus manus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Constantinus">Constantino</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Fuscarus">Fuscari</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Stephanus">Stefano</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name key="#Witness" ref="Vitalis">Vitale</name></persName>
                        rogatis testis.  + <rs key="#Writer">Scriptum</rs> livello per manum
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Victor"
                            >Victuri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> conplivi et dedi.  </ab>
                </div>
